--- 
title  : String::Mask
summary: String Algebra
license: Apache 2.0
authors: Thomas Sawyer
created: 2009-07-19

requires:
  - qed (test)
  - syckle (build)

description:
  String::Mask provides a kind-of string algebra
  useful for manipulating strings in in comparitive
  ways, eg. add, subtract, xor, etc.

